# Contribution #
################

@Node Contribution "How to contribute ?"

You can feel free to send @{"me" Link Adresses} :

-@{i}Articles@{ui}
 You can write some articles for me about whatever you want :
 - Your likes and dislikes about an album,
 - A concert report,
 - News and rumours about bands, albums, dates and so on

-@{i}Charts@{ui}
 I need your votes to create some charts about :
 - Albums,
 - Singles,
 - Bands,
 - Videos,
 - ...
 Please print the @{"vote form" Link vote} and send it back to @{"me" Link Adresses}.
 ( Same thing for articles ).
 A list of voters will also be published.

-@{i}Concert Dates@{ui}
 I will draw a  table  of concert dates for every country as far as I
 receive datas.

-@{i}Good Hard Rock modules to put on the disc@{ui}.

-@{i}Digitized pictures of albums'covers@{ui}.

-@{i}Adverts@{ui}.
 You want to publish an advert to promote your band, swap material or
 stuff ( music  stuff ), seek ( and  destroy ? ) some  HEAVY contacts
 or anything else ? Just send me your advert. It will be published in
 the next edition of Point & Rock.

Your articles must  be preferably  clear, ready to use ( i.e. on disc
or already printed ).
Everyone who send me an article on disc will receive the next edition
of Point & Rock on  his disc and will have his name in the greetings.

@endnode

