@Node Final "Final Words"

For the fourth time, I  must  tell  you : the  show is over ! But the
show will go on !!! I'll be back in ± 2  months  with  a new issue of
YOUR favourite magazine !

I have already  some ideas  for  next  edition, but shuuut !!! It's a
secret !!! I hope that what I want to do will be possible.

I  need  more  contribution  for  the  votes. Note to all voters : be
REGULAR ! When you  see  the  new edition has hit the street, fill in
another vote form. You  can  send  it  to me by snail or by E-mail...
I thanx here Nec and Dieter for their stuff ! I appreciated it.

Summer is approaching, and  also  the  long  awaited  festivals. This
year, a lot of bands will tour in Europe. I think to Aerosmith, Kiss,
Smashing Pumpkins... If you go to one of these festivals, think to me
and write an article ( I'll do it too :) ).

I hope next time I won't  have  to  announce  another split. It's the
second time that I have to. Maybe next time I will  tell you that YAB
( Yet Another Band ) is reforming...

That's it for today, I have nothing more to say, keep on rocking men,
and women !!! Enjoy life and music.

See you in Point & Rock 5.

And don't forget : Same old every day, if things don't  change you're
just gonna rot !!! ( Aerosmith - Get a Grip )



                                Yours, 
                                Mister No ^ aßS - 20/03/97


@endnode


